	<Name><![CDATA[RevenueStreamHijacking_Case2025_137857]]></Name>
	<Description><![CDATA[Multi-paradigm simulation of Revenue Stream Hijacking Case 2025-137857. Models the 6-phase criminal enterprise: Investment Motive (Ketoni ZAR 18.75M), Creditor Elimination, Infrastructure Seizure, Revenue Hijacking (R10.27M), Legal Weaponization (perjured interdict), and Evidence Destruction. Combines System Dynamics (financial flows), Discrete-Event Simulation (fraud event chain), and Agent-Based Modeling (perpetrator/victim behavior).]]></Description>
